(40, 15, 28, 45, 4, 19, 20, 'great is thy faith', 'Faith and Healing Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of faith leading to healing and fulfillment of promises. Both passages emphasize the strength of faith, with the woman receiving healing for her daughter and Abraham being strong in faith regarding God''s promises.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
